<text top="433" left="51" width="53" height="9" font="2">tematic error.</text>
<text top="445" left="62" width="227" height="9" font="2">Today, however, the effects of the charm quark in the sea</text>
<text top="458" left="51" width="238" height="9" font="2">are more and more systematically considered and most of the</text>
